reviewText:
The tape has a minor problem but not a big deal
with it it did surprise me but still a good video
My kids still love the classics. Its a shame that alot of these old ones are discontinued, Im still looking for Jay Jays colorful cover up.

Terrible. This is an early one so it is not animated like the ones you're used to--it is just still shots of air plane models that don't move or talk. It's very bad and I thought at first I had bought a bootleg or something. Stick to the new ones.
